<BaseLayout title="Affiliate Disclosure - 1H Crypto" lang="en" activeNav="disclosure">

<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
  <p class="text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-8">Last updated: May 2026</p>

  <div class="space-y-6 text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
    <div class="card p-6">
      <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">About Affiliate Links on This Site</h3>
      <p>Some links on this site are affiliate links. If you register, subscribe, or make a purchase through these links, I may earn a small commission at no additional cost to you. You may also receive exclusive discounts, cash rebates, or lower trading fees.</p>
      <p class="mt-3">All commissions are used solely for site maintenance, content updates, and server costs. Your costs are never increased, and your rights are never affected. Thank you for your support.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-6">
      <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Does This Affect My Analysis?</h3>
      <p>No. All analysis articles and simulated trading records are independently produced. I will not write fake positive reviews just because a platform pays a commission. If I stop using a tool, its affiliate link is removed.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-6">
      <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">How Many Things Do You Recommend?</h3>
      <p>Only things I genuinely use. I will not recommend products I haven't tested, and I will not push junk products for a commission.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-6">
      <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Which Platforms?</h3>
      <p class="mb-2">Affiliate links on this site currently involve:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
        <li>Binance — Commission: 20%-40% of referee's trading fees</li>
        <li>OKX — Commission: 30%-50% of referee's trading fees</li>
        <li>Bybit — Commission: 30%-50% of referee's trading fees</li>
        <li>Gate.io — Commission: 30%-60% of referee's trading fees</li>
        <li>TradingView — Commission: 30% of subscription fee</li>
        <li>Ledger — Commission: 10%-15% of hardware sales</li>
        <li>3Commas — Commission: 30% of subscription fee</li>
        <li>Bitsgap — Commission: 30% of subscription fee</li>
        <li>Coinrule — Commission: 25% of subscription fee</li>
        <li>Cryptohopper — Commission: 30% of subscription fee</li>
        <li>Koinly — Commission: 20%-30% of subscription fee</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-6">
      <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Sponsored Content</h3>
      <p>All technical analysis and simulated trading records on this site are original and not influenced by any platform, project, or advertiser. Sponsored content, if any, will be clearly disclosed at the top of the article. All opinions are my own and do not constitute financial advice.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-6">
